These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: white, blood-red, amber, coral, turquise, mauve, chestnut
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: ambient, blues, classical, disco, folk, house, salsa
7 different pets are kept: goldfish, snake, lizard, frog, turtle, cat, pony
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: october, september, march, august, june, april, may
 1. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
 2. the fan of disco is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is the owner of the turtle##1
 4. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 5. the fan of salsa is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the fan of house##1
 7. the fan of blues is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 9. the fan of classical is on the far right##1
10. the fan of classical is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
11. the person who likes mauve is in the middle##1
12. the person who likes amber is on the far left##1
13. the fan of folk is in the middle##1
14. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
15. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who likes white##1
16. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
17. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
18. the fan of classical is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
19. the person who's birthday is in march is in the middle##1
20. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
21. the fan of blues is on the right of the person who likes coral##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |    5     |     6      |       7       |
| Color      | amber    | white     | chestnut  | mauve   | coral | turquise      | blood-red          |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | disco   | house  | folk       | ambient  | blues      | classical     |
| Pet         | goldfish | snake | turtle | cat | lizard   | frog     | pony |
| Birthday     | may      | april   | october   | march  | august  | june | september       |

