 7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
 8. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person eating banana##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is the person eating artichoke##1
10. the person who's birthday is in may is in the middle##1
11. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
12. the person who's birthday is in november is the person driving the ship##1
13. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
14. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
15. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
16. the person who's birthday is in november is the person driving the ship##1
17. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
