There are 7 different nationalities: nigerian, colombian, italian, american, russian, brazilian, japanese
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: handball, ice-hockey, lacrosse, surfing, swimming, tennis, san-francisco-polo
 1. the person traveling to rome is the oliveros-smoker##1
 2. the nigerian is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
