10. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
11. the bolivar-smoker is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
12. the oliveros-smoker is the person who's sport is swimming##1
13. the person who's sport is san-francisco-polo is on the left of the american##1
14. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the brazilian##1
15. the bolivar-smoker is on the far right##1
16. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
17. the person traveling to prague is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
